{
  "page": "Gay Abandon",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Gay Abandon</b></i> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentoshi</a> cog during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gay_Abandon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Aegon_and_Viserys_at_the_Battle_of_the_Gullet_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/79/Aegon_and_Viserys_at_the_Battle_of_the_Gullet_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/350px-Aegon_and_Viserys_at_the_Battle_of_the_Gullet_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"248\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/79/Aegon_and_Viserys_at_the_Battle_of_the_Gullet_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/525px-Aegon_and_Viserys_at_the_Battle_of_the_Gullet_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/79/Aegon_and_Viserys_at_the_Battle_of_the_Gullet_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/700px-Aegon_and_Viserys_at_the_Battle_of_the_Gullet_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Aegon_and_Viserys_at_the_Battle_of_the_Gullet_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys II Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Gullet\" title=\"Battle of the Gullet\">Battle of the Gullet</a>, by Jota Saraiva</div></div></div>\n<p>Two <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">Targaryen</a> princes, <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon the Younger</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys II Targaryen\">Viserys</a>, were to be fostered by the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Pentos\" title=\"Prince of Pentos\">Prince of Pentos</a> near the start of the civil war. While carrying them to <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>, the <i>Gay Abandon</i> met ninety warships of the <a href=\"/index.php/Triarchy\" title=\"Triarchy\">Triarchy</a> sailing from the <a href=\"/index.php/Stepstones\" title=\"Stepstones\">Stepstones</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Gullet\" title=\"Gullet\">Gullet</a>. Aegon managed to fly away atop his dragon, <a href=\"/index.php/Stormcloud\" title=\"Stormcloud\">Stormcloud</a>, but Viserys remaining behind. Viserys was eventually captured by a <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyroshi</a> captain who brought him to <a href=\"/index.php/Sharako_Lohar\" title=\"Sharako Lohar\">Sharako Lohar</a>, the Triarchy's admiral. Shortly thereafter the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Gullet\" title=\"Battle of the Gullet\">Battle of the Gullet</a> took place.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The fate of Viserys remained unknown to his family until his return to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> five years later.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gay_Abandon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - The Red Dragon and the Gold.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Voyage of Alyn Oakenfist.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404194738\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.030 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.053 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 222/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8599/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 884/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 528/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1413/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.52 MB/50 MB\nL